lead_paragraph: Harking back to a previous era and ripping up a text book full of received wisdom, Leicester City's remarkable title triumph has been founded on a footballing philosophy that many had consigned to the dustbin.

headline.print_headline: Ranieri Turns Back the Clock to Make Leicester Champions
